window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Luca Would you risk it all—your career, your dream, your life—to save a stranger?</p> <p>I would. I did.</p> <p>Except, in saving her, I destroyed any chance at living out the future I was destined for.</p> <p>They say what I did was reckless. What they don’t know is that I’d do it all again if it meant meeting her. My bellezza.</p> <p>Katarina</p> <p>Death threats are supposed to stay threats. It comes with being in the public eye.</p> <p>I never expected anyone to actually follow through on their plan to kill me.</p> <p>A plan they would have succeeded in completing… if it weren’t for him.</p> <p>Luca Valentino.I owe him my life. But it’s my heart he’s taking.</p> <p>This is book four in a series of standalone mafia romances. Each book contains the story of one of the four sons of Theo and Holly Valentino, you can listen about them in The Valentino Empire Series.</p>"; 
